<NEW>

There was another huge roar from GRIMLOCK as he heard WHEELIE's
bantor, his smaller arms flailing as he bashed into a tree with his
powerful tail. "Me Grimlock am own master!" He growled. "No one give
order to me Grimlock except for Gimlock!"

"Yeah!" SLUDGE said, "You Grimlock am in charge. "Me follow you!"

SNARL growled and nodded his head, only looking at GRIMLOCK and then
nodded in acquiescence.

Growling SLAG turned to look at WHEELIE, "Me Slag say smash
everything, smash everyone no matter what! No one tell us what to do!"

That was of course followed by a roar of agreement from SLUDGE and SNARL.

GRIMLOCK looked at WHEELIE his optics flickering as if he were
fighting for control of something. "Me Grimlock say smash!" and then
he growled incoherently.

SLAG looked at WHEELIE and started to charge him!

This was followed quickly enough by SNARL and then SLUDGE!

(TAG)

- Preston
